title: Bandai Tamashii Nations S.H. Figuarts Leonardo "Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles" Action Figure
feature: The leader and most pragmatic of the brothers, Leonardo; Strategic use of die-cast material is used for realism in the buckle and weight in the legs
Leonardo's set includes his iconic katana (x2), interchangeable head, interchangeable hands (x6), weapon holding parts, and manhole covers (x2)
Product is official and carries the Bluefin Distribution logo
description: You might as well call us Tamashii Turtle Nations when you see what's in store for S.H.Figuarts. The first ever S.H.Figuarts version of everyone's favorite Teenage Mutants are coming in the classic animation colors! Each sold separately with the other Turtles coming out later this year! Get your cowabunga on S.H.Figuarts style (and grab some pizza while you're at it too).
